169
00:14:38,340 --> 00:14:43,580
♪The vortex
that confuses time and space♪

170
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:50,380
♪Looking back at you and me♪

171
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:59,300
♪I'm looking for your dream♪

172
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:05,620
♪In every time and space♪

173
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:12,220
