♪Will you still remember me?♪

178
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:19,540
♪I'm looking for your dream♪

179
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:26,300
♪In every time and space♪

180
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:32,620
♪Yet I never catch up♪

181
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:39,140
♪With the spring wind♪

182
00:16:42,759 --> 00:16:45,559
Turns out the hero I admire

183
00:16:45,559 --> 00:16:47,039
has been right by my side.

184
00:16:52,279 --> 00:16:53,039
Do you know why

185
00:16:53,039 --> 00:16:54,360
I went to Yuchun Theater?

186
00:16:55,679 --> 00:16:56,440
Why?

187
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:00,000
Because

188
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,720
I couldn't watch you die again.

189
00:17:22,039 --> 00:17:23,519
Zhou Chi,

190
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:25,640
I didn't see you today,

191
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:28,039
so you don't meddle in my business.

192
00:17:51,079 --> 00:17:51,920
Sorry.

193
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,559
I should've realized it sooner.

194
00:17:55,079 --> 00:17:56,359
Why are you apologizing?

195
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,319
If I had realized earlier,

196
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:05,559
I could've protected you better.

197
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:09,079
Haven't you been protecting me
all this time?

198
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,599
I could still do better.

199
00:18:17,319 --> 00:18:18,119
(Zhou Chi,)

200
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,519
(are you my good luck?)

201
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,799
Chi,

202
00:18:26,599 --> 00:18:27,240
when the day comes

203
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,790
that South City no longer needs
the King of Hearts,

204
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,500
let's leave this place together.

205
00:18:32,079 --> 00:18:32,880
Sure.

